y.io.graphml.graph2d
Class Graph2DGraphMLHandler

java.lang.Object
  y.io.graphml.GraphMLHandler
      y.io.graphml.graph2d.Graph2DGraphMLHandler

public class Graph2DGraphMLHandler
extends GraphMLHandler

This class adds configuration to GraphMLHandler for handling Graph2D instances.

The following configuration is added:

  • Uses implementations of GraphElementFactory and HierarchySupport that handle hierarchy information from HierarchyManager, and set/write Realizer information.
  • Registers input and output handlers for reading and writing Realizer information, as well as default NodeRealizerSerializer and EdgeRealizerSerializer implementations for all Realizers in the core yFiles library. Registers (de)serialization callbacks for labels, embedded images and other common content.
  • Supports handling of embedded resources.
  • Supports postprocessor input and output handling.
  • Adds convenience methods for registration of custom NodeRealizerSerializer and EdgeRealizerSerializer instances.
